Play It Safe Instructions:

Find a park that's safe to play at (in Ballarat!)

Download the Play it Safe CSV (Only currently available for Ballarat) from this URL:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B0xEHxNpsK2STVk1OFhSbzhncWc/view?usp=sharing

Drag and drop it on to the map at http://map.terria.io/

Click around to see which parks are safe, find a park with a low safety score near you.  Check out if the abundance of CCTV cameras, schools or graffiti is high in the area.  

Choose a park, get out there and Play It Safe.

